alert-level-announcement = Attention! Station alert level is now {$name}! {$announcement}

alert-level-unknown = Unknown.
alert-level-unknown-instructions = Unknown.

alert-level-alpha = Alpha
alert-level-alpha-announcement = It is now safe to return to your workplaces.
alert-level-alpha-instructions = Do your job.

alert-level-enigma = Enigma
alert-level-enigma-announcement = There is a confirmed threat to the station. Security should perform random checks. Crewmembers are advised to be vigilant and report suspicious activity to security.
alert-level-enigma-instructions = Crewmembers are advised to be vigilant and report suspicious activity to security.

alert-level-sigma = Sigma
alert-level-sigma-announcement = There is an immediate threat to the station. Security should prepare to use lethal force if necessary. Crewmembers should find a safe place to shelter in, and are advised to follow any present authorities.
alert-level-sigma-instructions = Crewmembers should find a safe place to shelter in, and are advised to follow any present authorities.

alert-level-tau = Tau
alert-level-tau-announcement = There is a structural or atmospheric threat within the station. Engineering staff are advised to immediately respond and perform safety measures. Crewmembers are advised to stay away from the threat, and stay in their workplaces if necessary.
alert-level-tau-instructions = Crewmembers are advised to stay away from the threat, and stay in their workplaces if necessary.

alert-level-kappa = Kappa
alert-level-kappa-announcement = A serious engineering or operational threat has been detected aboard the station. Responsible departments are ordered to contain the source immediately. Crewmembers should avoid hazardous areas and follow command instructions.
alert-level-kappa-instructions = Leave hazardous areas. Follow command and departmental instructions.

alert-level-gamma = Gamma
alert-level-gamma-announcement = Eidos Empire has ordered the Gamma security level on the station. Security is to have weapons equipped at all times, and all civilians are to immediately seek their nearest head for transportation to a secure location.
alert-level-gamma-instructions = All civilians are to immediately seek their nearest head for transportation to a secure location.

alert-level-delta = Delta
alert-level-delta-announcement = The station is currently under threat of imminent destruction. Crewmembers are advised to listen to heads of staff for more information.
alert-level-delta-instructions = Crewmembers are advised to listen to heads of staff for more information.

alert-level-epsilon = Epsilon
alert-level-epsilon-announcement = Eidos Empire has ordered the Epsilon security level on the station. Consider all contracts terminated.
alert-level-epsilon-instructions = Consider all contracts terminated.
